name: Sombra (Overwatch) LORA
description:
Version 2 is overall big improvment. Simply prompting for Sombra will suffice for whole look, except for optional lipstick.

Suitable strength range is 0.6-0.8. Triggers for paticular things, in case you still need them, are:

  • Outfit - bodysuit, coat, trench coat, turtleneck, high collar, legwear, gloves, short sleeves

  • Accesories - jewelry, stud earrings, hologram, holographic interface

  • Makeup - makeup, mascara, eyeshadow, eyeliner, long fingernails, nail polish

  • Gun (really wonky, not trained for it) - holding gun, weapon, submachine gun, finger on trigger

If you liked my work, you can donate here.

Trained on Anything V4.5.

Samples are 512x768, not cherry picked, without HighRes.fix, using OrangeCocoa 50/50 Mix , with OrangeMix VAE (for version 2), and using EasyNegative embedding. Inpaint examples are txt2img with 1 single inpaint done on eyes.

modelVersions.name: v.2
modelVersions.description: Tighter, more quality revised dataset of 30 pictures with deepbooru tags, less size, easier to use. Cleaner look, wide image issue should be resolved. Simply prompting for Sombra will suffice for whole look, except for optional lipstick. Lipstick optional cause it's kinda strong.
